<hr data-start="179" data-end="182">
<h1 data-section-id="hbwuta" data-start="184" data-end="217">Step 1: Create a GitHub Account</h1>
<h3 data-section-id="fs9yh4" data-start="219" data-end="237">1. Open GitHub</h3>
<p data-start="238" data-end="244">Go to:</p>
<p data-start="246" data-end="268"><strong data-start="246" data-end="268"><a data-start="248" data-end="266" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link" href="https://github.com/">https://github.com<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none select-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75] select-none"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-28b72de4.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></strong></p>
<h3 data-section-id="vef5ia" data-start="270" data-end="294"><span role="text">2. Click <strong data-start="283" data-end="294">Sign up</strong></span></h3>
<p data-start="296" data-end="356">You will see the <strong data-start="313" data-end="324">Sign up</strong> button in the top-right corner.</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1gc3yjk" data-start="358" data-end="383">3. Enter your details</h3>
<p data-start="385" data-end="393">Fill in:</p>
<ul data-start="395" data-end="478">
<li data-section-id="18lefxu" data-start="395" data-end="410">
<p data-start="397" data-end="410">Email Address</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1i84dqv" data-start="411" data-end="421">
<p data-start="413" data-end="421">Password</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="15zgabp" data-start="422" data-end="457">
<p data-start="424" data-end="457">Username (Example: <code data-start="443" data-end="456">ruchitha123</code>)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="11ojbhy" data-start="458" data-end="478">
<p data-start="460" data-end="478">Country (if asked)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-section-id="1vo13me" data-start="480" data-end="504">4. Verify your email</h3>
<p data-start="506" data-end="544">GitHub will send a verification email.</p>
<p data-start="546" data-end="597">Open your email and click <strong data-start="572" data-end="596">Verify email address</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="599" data-end="632">Your GitHub account is now ready.</p>
<hr data-start="634" data-end="637">
<h1 data-section-id="76qqo7" data-start="639" data-end="660">Step 2: Install Git</h1>
<p data-start="662" data-end="722">Git is the software that connects your computer with GitHub.</p>
<h3 data-section-id="loweco" data-start="724" data-end="740">Download Git</h3>
<p data-start="742" data-end="748">Go to:</p>
<p data-start="750" data-end="779"><a data-start="750" data-end="779" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link" href="https://git-scm.com/downloads">https://git-scm.com/downloads<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none select-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75] select-none"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-28b72de4.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
<p data-start="781" data-end="810">Download the Windows version.</p>
<p data-start="812" data-end="861">Install it by clicking <strong data-start="835" data-end="843">Next</strong> until <strong data-start="850" data-end="860">Finish</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="863" data-end="889">Keep the default settings.</p>
<hr data-start="891" data-end="894">
<h1 data-section-id="1azx0ok" data-start="896" data-end="931">Step 3: Check if Git is Installed</h1>
<p data-start="933" data-end="965">Open <strong data-start="938" data-end="956">Command Prompt</strong> and type</p>
