<p data-start="93" data-end="193">Based on your report, I'll help you create a <strong data-start="138" data-end="192">complete GitHub-ready Blood Bank Management System</strong>.</p>
<h3 data-section-id="7ym86a" data-start="195" data-end="214">Here's the plan</h3>
