ide\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light packing layout image for a rainy trip, with simple item icons and empty spaces I can tick or label myself.\"},{\"body\":\"For Rath Yatra 2026, explain the main terms, the chariot symbolism and what a first-time observer should know respectfully.\",\"title\":\"Learn Rath Yatra basics\"},{\"body\":\"Practise a behavioural interview answer with me using STAR. Ask me for the role and one experience, then coach my first draft.\",\"title\":\"Practise an interview answer\"},{\"body\":\"Create a text-light Van Mahotsav sapling care card with icons for water, sun, pruning, and a blank plant name.\",\"title\":\"Make sapling care cards\"},{\"title\":\"Draw my monsoon bag map\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light monsoon bag map for my commute. Ask my city first, then make it simple, bright and printable.\"},{\"title\":\"Design a morning routine\",\"body\":\"Help me design a morning routine I can actually follow. Ask one question about my start time, then suggest a simple first week.\"},{\"title\":\"Draw a calmer desk layout\",\"body\":\"Create a simple top-down desk layout with zones for work, charging and stationery. Use icons and blank labels, not tiny text.\"},{\"body\":\"Turn my trip packing into a one-bag game. Ask where I’m going and for how many days, then give a compact list with “skip it” notes.\",\"title\":\"Pack one bag without drama\"},{\"body\":\"Create a low-stakes FIFA World Cup prediction game for friends, with simple rules and a blank score table.\",\"title\":\"Make a World Cup prediction game\"},{\"title\":\"Cook with fewer tomatoes\",\"body\":\"Plan a tomato-light Indian dinner. Give swaps for dal, sabzi and chutney, and ask what staples I have only if needed.\"},{\"body\":\"Create a simple text-light kitchen card showing tomato-light swaps for dal, sabzi and chutney. Use icons and blank labels, no brand names.\",\"title\":\"Draw tomato-light swaps\"},{\"title\":\"Decode the monsoon map\",\"body\":\"Ask my city, then explain today’s monsoon progress using official sources and what it may mean for the next few days.\"},{\"title\":\"Pack for a rainy trip\",\"body\":\"Make a practical packing list for a rainy trip. Ask me where I’m going and for how many days before you start.\"},{\"body\":\"Help me plan an F1 2026 race weekend watch setup in India. Ask which race and whether I’ll watch solo or with friends.\",\"title\":\"Set up an F1 race weekend\"},{\"title\":\"Make a yatra checklist card\",\"body\":\"Create a simple, text-light Rath Yatra trip checklist card with icons for water, ID, medicines, and phone charging.\"},{\"title\":\"Make mornings run on rails\",\"body\":\"Turn my morning into a low-stress routine game. Ask what time I need to leave, then build a simple countdown with buffer.\"},{\"body\":\"Build a party playlist mood from current Indian YouTube music trends. Blend nostalgic Hindi and regional DJ energy without repeating one style.\",\"title\":\"Shape a nostalgia playlist\"},{\"body\":\"I can upload a photo or describe the area. Give me a 30-minute declutter plan with keep, move, donate and discard steps.\",\"title\":\"Declutter a small space\"},{\"body\":\"Create a text-light interview story board with 5 blank cards. Ask my target role first, then keep it simple and editable.\",\"title\":\"Map my interview stories\"},{\"title\":\"Plan a home move\",\"body\":\"Make a moving checklist for an Indian city apartment. Ask my move date and whether packers are involved before drafting.\"},{\"body\":\"Make a 7-day study plan for a topic I need to revise. Ask the subject and time I can spare each day.\",\"title\":\"Plan a 7-day study sprint\"},{\"title\":\"Prep a cricket group chat\",\"body\":\"Make a spoiler-free group chat primer for India’s next Women’s T20 World Cup match. Include form, stakes and 3 talking points.\"},{\"title\":\"Map storage zones\",\"body\":\"Create a simple storage-zone image for a shelf or cupboard, using blank labels and clear icons for where things should go.\"},{\"body\":\"Make a practical packing plan for a trip. Ask my destination and number of days, then group items by bag.\",\"title\":\"Pack for a trip neatly\"},{\"title\":\"Catch up on Women’s T20\",\"body\":\"Give me a quick Women’s T20 World Cup catch-up for India’s campaign. Explain standings, key fixtures and what to watch next.\"},{\"title\":\"Remix a dance hook safely\",\"body\":\"Make three original Reel ideas for a new Bollywood dance song trend. No copied steps or lyrics, just fresh prompts.\"},{\"body\":\"Help me choose a monsoon weekend trip in India. Ask my starting city, then compare safer rain-season options and what to avoid.\",\"title\":\"Pick a safer monsoon break\"},{\"title\":\"Pick a World Cup match\",\"body\":\"Check the current FIFA World Cup fixtures and suggest one match for me to watch in India, with a quick reason and a fun talking point.\"},{\"body\":\"Teach me 5 Indian monsoon snacks, what makes each work with chai, and one easier home version for each.\",\"title\":\"Learn monsoon snack logic\"},{\"title\":\"Find a weekend trip idea\",\"body\":\"Help me plan a relaxed weekend trip. Ask my starting city and travel style, then suggest 3 realistic India options.\"},{\"title\":\"Create a party vibe card\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light party vibe card image inspired by current India music trends. Use abstract shapes, no artists or logos.\"},{\"title\":\"Turn study into a mini quest\",\"body\":\"Make a 7-day mini quest for learning one topic. Ask me the topic, then split it into tiny missions and a final boss quiz.\"},{\"title\":\"Visualise a simple dinner plan\",\"body\":\"Create a simple, text-light visual cooking plan from my ingredients. Ask me for a fridge photo or short list first.\"},{\"title\":\"Start watching Wimbledon\",\"body\":\"Give me a beginner’s guide to Wimbledon 2026: how the draw works, who to watch, and which matches are friendly for India timings.\"},{\"title\":\"Make a monsoon bag card\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light visual card for my monsoon commute bag. Use simple icons and leave space for me to add city-specific notes.\"},{\"title\":\"Draft a warm short speech\",\"body\":\"Help me write a short speech that sounds warm and natural. Ask the occasion first, then make a clean first draft.\"},{\"body\":\"Create a text-light packing grid for a short trip, using simple icons and blank labels. Ask the trip length first.\",\"title\":\"Create a packing grid\"},{\"title\":\"Create a football watch badge\",\"body\":\"Create a simple World Cup watch badge image with blank space for my chosen team, match time, and snacks. No official logos.\"},{\"body\":\"Make an India-friendly FIFA World Cup watch plan for the next week, with sensible sleep trade-offs and one must-watch match.\",\"title\":\"Tame the late kick-offs\"},{\"body\":\"Help me decide whether to attend Puri Rath Yatra. Ask my starting city, then make a practical travel and crowd-safety plan.\",\"title\":\"Plan a Rath Yatra visit\"},{\"title\":\"Make a Rath Yatra quiz\",\"body\":\"Create a gentle Rath Yatra quiz for a family chat, with easy questions, answers, and one thing to learn from each.\"},{\"body\":\"I’ll paste a message. Make it warm, clear and natural in Indian English, with 3 options from polite to casual.\",\"title\":\"Polish my WhatsApp tone\"},{\"body\":\"Use BMPS 2026 as an example to teach how esports points tables, placement points and kill points work.\",\"title\":\"Read an esports points table\"},{\"title\":\"Decode a T20 scorecard\",\"body\":\"Use the latest India women’s T20 World Cup scorecard to explain run rate, wickets and phases for a new fan.\"},{\"body\":\"Explain how streaming charts, platform drops and social buzz differ, using current India OTT examples.\",\"title\":\"Understand OTT buzz\"},{\"title\":\"Create a match-night snack board\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light image of a cosy football snack board for a home watch night. Use simple team-colour accents, no logos or player likenesses.\"},{\"title\":\"Decode the Lord’s Test buzz\",\"body\":\"Explain why India Women’s Lord’s Test is a big deal, then give me three playful talking points for a cricket chat.\"},{\"title\":\"Help me choose without overthinking\",\"body\":\"I’m stuck on an everyday choice. Ask me to list the options, then run a quick playful decision game with pros, trade-offs and a final pick.\"},{\"title\":\"Plan snacks for guests\",\"body\":\"Help me plan easy snacks and drinks for guests. Ask how many people and what I can cook, then suggest a balanced menu.\"},{\"body\":\"Help me read a packaged food label. I can upload a photo or type the ingredients, nutrition table and dates.\",\"title\":\"Read a food label\"},{\"title\":\"Draw a snack board\",\"body\":\"Create a simple rainy snack-board image from the items I list. Keep it text-light, cosy and realistic.\"},{\"title\":\"Compare appliance specs\",\"body\":\"Upload a photo or paste the specs for two appliances. Explain the terms and make a comparison table without telling me what to buy.\"},{\"title\":\"Reset your rainy entryway\",\"body\":\"Make a 10-minute monsoon entryway reset for wet shoes, umbrellas and bags. Include a no-shopping version for a small flat.\"},{\"title\":\"Cook with what you have\",\"body\":\"I can upload a fridge photo or list ingredients. Suggest 3 simple meals I can cook today and what I may need to buy.\"},{\"body\":\"Help me turn what I have into dinner. Ask me for a fridge photo or ingredient list, then suggest 2 simple options.\",\"title\":\"Make dinner from what��s at home\"},{\"title\":\"Run a mock interview\",\"body\":\"Act as my interviewer for a role I’m applying to. Ask the role first, then give one question at a time with feedback.\"},{\"title\":\"Make a monsoon commute card\",\"body\":\"Create a simple icon-only monsoon commute card for India: rain alert, route check, power bank, shoes, ID, water. Keep labels blank.\"},{\"body\":\"Make a 10-minute weekly home check for dengue prevention. Focus on coolers, pots, drains and stored water, without medical advice.\",\"title\":\"Check mosquito breeding spots\"},{\"title\":\"Make a tennis watch planner\",\"body\":\"Create a simple grass-court watch planner image with blank match slots. Keep it text-light, with no logos.\"},{\"title\":\"Decode a flat listing\",\"body\":\"Paste a flat listing. Explain 1RK, deposit, maintenance and brokerage, then give me 5 smart questions to ask.\"},{\"title\":\"Read today’s rain alerts\",\"body\":\"Teach me how to read IMD rain alerts for my city and turn them into a simple commute plan. Ask my city first if needed.\"},{\"body\":\"Without spoilers, help me decide if Raakh is too heavy for tonight. If yes, suggest a lighter watch mood instead.\",\"title\":\"Pick my OTT mood\"},{\"title\":\"Summarise a document\",\"body\":\"Upload a PDF or paste the text. Summarise it in plain English and list the key decisions, dates and action items.\"},{\"title\":\"Create a chariot craft sheet\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light Rath Yatra chariot craft sheet image with simple shapes and blank labels, no deity likenesses.\"},{\"title\":\"Explain a warranty clearly\",\"body\":\"Explain this warranty in plain English. I’ll upload a photo or paste the key lines. Point out questions to ask, without giving legal advice.\"},{\"title\":\"Tidy your digital files\",\"body\":\"Create a folder system for my digital files. Ask what I mostly store, then suggest folder names and simple rules.\"},{\"title\":\"Make a reading routine card\",\"body\":\"Create a calm, text-light visual card for a 20-minute reading routine, with simple step icons and space for handwritten notes.\"},{\"body\":\"Help me make a CUET college preference shortlist. Ask my course first, then create a comparison table I can fill.\",\"title\":\"Build a CUET shortlist\"},{\"title\":\"Decode Wimbledon scoring\",\"body\":\"Teach me Wimbledon scoring like I’m watching for the first time, with a playful mini quiz at the end.\"},{\"title\":\"Sketch a rainy snack platter\",\"body\":\"Create a cosy, text-light image of an Indian monsoon snack platter for home inspiration. No brand names or readable labels.\"},{\"title\":\"Build a spoiler-free watchlist\",\"body\":\"Help me make a spoiler-free OTT watchlist from current India releases. Ask my preferred language or mood, then suggest what to try first.\"},{\"title\":\"Make a snack tasting sheet\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light monsoon snack tasting sheet with five blank slots, simple spice and crunch icons, and no brand names.\"},{\"body\":\"Show me a 15-second Reel structure for teaching one small idea. Ask me for the topic first, then make a shot-by-shot plan.\",\"title\":\"Practise a 15-second Reel\"},{\"body\":\"I’ll paste a board-style answer. Improve it for marks, keep my points, and show a 3-line examiner-friendly version.\",\"title\":\"Improve a board answer\"},{\"title\":\"Check if a FASTag pass helps\",\"body\":\"Help me decide if the FASTag Annual Pass is worth checking. Ask my vehicle type and usual highway trips, then compare fit, not exact savings.\"},{\"body\":\"Help me make a travel-day plan with buffer time, snacks and document checks. Ask the journey type first.\",\"title\":\"Plan a calmer travel day\"},{\"title\":\"Plan a no-bore tiffin week\",\"body\":\"Make my next 5 tiffins feel less repetitive. Ask me for a kitchen photo or ingredient list, then suggest easy mix-and-match ideas.\"},{\"title\":\"Reset a messy space\",\"body\":\"Help me reset a messy desk or room. Ask for a photo or short description, then give me a 20-minute plan.\"},{\"title\":\"Plan a no-fuss tiffin week\",\"body\":\"Plan 5 simple tiffin ideas using Indian home staples. Ask who it is for and any food restrictions before making the plan.\"},{\"body\":\"My train ticket is WL or RAC. Explain what it means and help me plan a backup without guessing confirmation chances.\",\"title\":\"Plan around a waitlisted ticket\"},{\"title\":\"Prepare a hard conversation\",\"body\":\"Help me prepare for a difficult conversation. Ask who it is with, then draft a calm opening and likely replies.\"},{\"title\":\"Pack for a monsoon train\",\"body\":\"Make a monsoon train carry-on list for my route. Ask destination and train class first, then keep it one-bag friendly.\"},{\"body\":\"Create a text-light Rath Yatra learning graphic with three simple chariots, symbol icons and blank labels. No faces or logos.\",\"title\":\"Make a chariot explainer\"},{\"body\":\"I want a rainy-day snack at home. I can upload a kitchen photo or list 3 ingredients. Suggest one quick option and a chai pairing.\",\"title\":\"Plan a monsoon snack\"},{\"body\":\"Help me pick a fun neutral team to follow at the FIFA World Cup. Ask one question first, then give a playful shortlist.\",\"title\":\"Pick my World Cup side quest\"},{\"body\":\"Give me a beginner-friendly Wimbledon 2026 guide for watching from India. Explain the format, terms and matches to follow.\",\"title\":\"Get into Wimbledon\"},{\"body\":\"Create a simple concept map for a topic I’m studying. Ask me the topic first, then keep the image text-light.\",\"title\":\"Draw a concept map\"},{\"title\":\"Make a simple society notice\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light notice graphic for an apartment water or power issue. Use blank space for timing and contact details outside the image.\"},{\"body\":\"Teach me how to choose monsoon-friendly fabrics and footwear for daily wear, without assuming my budget or city.\",\"title\":\"Choose monsoon-friendly fabric\"},{\"title\":\"Try a regional film night\",\"body\":\"Find a current Indian regional trailer that suits a light film night, then suggest a no-spoiler watch plan.\"},{\"title\":\"Draft a society notice\",\"body\":\"Draft a polite apartment-society notice for a water cut. Ask me the date and duration first, then write group-message and notice-board versions.\"},{\"body\":\"Create a text-light tiffin idea wheel with simple food icons and blank labels. Ask my main flavour preference first.\",\"title\":\"Make a tiffin idea wheel\"},{\"body\":\"Help me prepare for a Passport Seva appointment. Ask which service it is, then make an official-doc checklist and visit-day plan.\",\"title\":\"Prep for Passport Seva\"},{\"body\":\"Create a simple budget bucket diagram with generic icons and three blank labels. Keep any written guidance outside the image.\",\"title\":\"Draw your budget buckets\"},{\"title\":\"Understand an ODI chase\",\"body\":\"Use a recent India ODI scorecard to teach me how a chase is paced: powerplay, middle overs, required run rate and wickets.\"},{\"title\":\"Sort ITR papers before filing\",\"body\":\"Help me make an ITR document folder for AY 2026-27. Ask only my income type first, then list likely documents to collect.\"},{\"title\":\"Sort my paperwork pile\",\"body\":\"Help me sort a pile of bills, forms and notes. Ask what categories I see, then give me a quick filing plan.\"},{\"title\":\"Explain the 48-team chaos\",\"body\":\"Explain the 48-team World Cup format like I’m joining a group chat late, with a tiny glossary and a playful example.\"},{\"title\":\"Learn women’s T20 terms\",\"body\":\"Explain five T20 cricket terms I’ll hear during India Women’s matches, with examples from the current World Cup.\"},{\"title\":\"Choose a Reel soundtrack\",\"body\":\"Find a current Indian music trend for a short video idea. Ask what the video is about, then suggest a clean hook and caption.\"},{\"title\":\"Draw a UPI payment flow\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light doodle showing when to use cash, UPI Lite or normal UPI. Check current rules first.\"}]},\"is_device_based\":true,\"passed\":true},\"3561896342\":{\"name\":\"3561896342\",\"rule_id\":\"default\",\"secondary_exposures\":[],\"id_type\":\"stableID\",\"value\":{\"pioneer\":[],\"wayfinder\":[],\"trailblazer\":[],\"seeker\":[],\"maverick\":[],\"stratos\":[]},\"is_device_based\":true,\"passed\":false},\"3203804112\":{\"name\":\"3203804112\",\"rule_id\":\"l1cQvHcaNrOGLwWcVswwT\",\"secondary_